\s MWAMI WANJE UMPUMURE AMASO
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Mwami wanje umpumure amaso, mbon’inzira ica k’umusaraba, niy’ishikana mw’ijuru ku Mana, niho tuzorangiriz’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd urugendo, turirimbe tugushime.\bd*
\pc \bdit Har’inzira nyinshi cane, zica ku musoz’unyerera, zimanuka zij’ikuzimu, benshi nizo ba camwo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Mbeg’iyo nzira imeze gute, yuzuy’umuco mwinshi cane, n’abayicamwo bameze gute, n’abahawe gucika abanab b’Imana, bavutse ubwa kabiri.\bd*
\pc \bdit Har’inzira nyinshi cane, zica ku musoz’unyerera, zimanuka zij’ikuzimu, benshi nizo ba camwo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Benshi baseng’Imana ariko inzira, ntibayibona, benshi bakunda Imana arikw’inzira ntibayibona ar’inzira y’ukuri kand’ishikana mu bugingo budashira.\bd*
\pc \bdit Har’inzira nyinshi cane, zica ku musoz’unyerera, zimanuka zij’ikuzimu, benshi nizo ba camwo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Wibuk’Isirayeli igeze mu bugaragwa, yari kumwe n’inkingi y’umuriro, yari kumwe na Mose umuhanuzi? Arikw’inzira ntibayibona.\bd*
\pc \bdit Har’inzira nyinshi cane, zica ku musoz’unyerera, zimanuka zij’ikuzimu, benshi nizo ba camwo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Batuka Mose inkingi ihari, bagator’amabuye inkigi ihari, bama bidodomba ibihe vyose, amaso yabo ntiyabon’Imana, kand’ariyo yari yarabahamagaye.\bd*
\pc \bdit Har’inzira nyinshi cane, zica ku musoz’unyerera, zimanuka zij’ikuzimu, benshi nizo ba camwo.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Mwami fash’\bd*\bd I\bd*\bd shengero ryawe twugurur’amaso tubone, tubon’inkingi y’umuriro, n’ukunt’irongor’ishengero m’ukuri kwose, dufashe Mwami tukuyoboke.\bd*
\pc \bdit Har’inzira nyinshi cane, zica ku musoz’unyerera, zimanuka zij’ikuzimu, benshi nizo ba camwo.\bdit*
